Kyle lives down the street but his mom doesnt trust him so who knows what im going to do with him. But i guess it could be worse; i mean his dad could still live down i Florida and i would NEVER be able to see him. well i am very bored and tired, i woke up this morning to the phone ringing and when someone didnt answer it i noticed that i was the only one home. that was wired because usually someone tells me that they are leaving so im clued in. But it was my mom that was the last on to leave this morning so i understand why i woke up clueless. its very cloudy outside which is cool but i hope it turns into a thunderstorm because those are really cool and i hope the power goes out cuz that will give me an excuse to not doo anythingaround the house.
